parameters: "Oh, Rise-chan. Did you bring a friend with you today?"

"But this is troubling. I don't have any interest in playing
with men, though."
"   I've come to capture you today."

"After that, you're going to spill everything about the
human trafficking connections and the information about the
underground organizations you know."

"Oh my, the usually obedient Rise-chan has become quite
defiant, hasn't she?"
"Fufu, does this mean you need to be punished again?"
"It's useless. Rise is no longer affected by brainwashing."

"I see. I don't know how you did it, but it certainly seems
like the brainwashing has been undone."

"But, well, if that's the case, it just means there's more
fun to be had in retraining you, right?"

"Hehe, this time, even without hypnosis, I'll make sure
you'll never think of defying me again."

"I'll thoroughly punish you and teach you what you really
are, okay? Rise-chan"

"   Hmph, do you really think you can do that now that I'm
not brainwashed?"

"Fufufu, even if you say that, your body is trembling,
wanting to be played with by me again. Right, Rise-chan?"

"But, well, it would be impossible for me to capture Rise-
chan by myself."
"That's why I made friends for times like this."

"Heheh, it just so happens that this girl and Rise-chan were
quite close, weren't they?"

"This girl was one of my favorite toys among the orphans.
She worked hard because she wanted to be like Rise-chan, so
she's become very strong, you know?"
"But, well, I guess even Rise-chan can't win against her."

"Fufu!! But if there's one advantage, it's that she won't
stop fighting until I tell her to, even if she gets hurt."

"Fufufu, I wonder if Rise-chan will crush this girl who
admired her and worked so hard, until she can no longer
move?"

"Well, if you surrender quietly, this girl won't come to any
harm, right?"

"Rise, there's no need to listen to him. I came along for
times like this."

"All Rise needs to do is stop that girl's movements
temporarily."
"Hmph, alright. If you say so, I'll trust you."

Suelle fires a bullet without hesitation from a gun-shaped
device at the brainwashed girl.

The bullet hits the girl and transforms into a net of light
that wraps around her body.
"Phew... It seems to have been a success."

"I thoroughly brainwashed and hypnotized her to fight even
when unconscious, turning her into a toy that won't stop
fighting!!"

"It's an application of the device we used to undo Rise's
brainwashing."

"Normally, you have to touch directly with the device to
undo the brainwashing. But that would require time to
restrain them to undo the brainwashing."

"So I thought about sending brainwashing commands of a
similar wavelength to temporarily overwrite the instructions
and cause confusion."

"But, even if you send similar instructions, it's ancient
magic... To prepare something like that in such a short
time..."

"Deciphering the spell completely would indeed be impossible
in the time we had."

"But thanks to the data we got from Rise, we could analyze
at least the wavelength pattern affected by the
instructions."
"No, I think you're the only one who could do that."

"Heh, well, that's fine. More importantly... Nolz? You're
prepared, right?"

"Wait, please wait!! Ahh, I apologize!! I'll apologize, so
please!!"
"Huh? Apologizing is a given, isn't it?"

"Eeeek!! I'll also provide information!! So please, forgive
me!!"

"You'll naturally spill the information. And after that, I'm
going to beat you down."
Rise: "Hmph, well... I'll leave it at this for now."
Rise: "Later we'll take you back and have a thorough talk."

Suelle: (He's already beaten to a pulp... Is he even in a
state to talk about his connections behind the scenes?)

And so, Rise and Suelle obtained a lead on information
connected to the human trafficking organization.

Meanwhile, at that time, in the basement of a certain
facility...
